move all the data to input view

adapt to iOS:
    You must request notification permissions. Add this to your Info.plist:
        <key>UIBackgroundModes</key>
        <array>
            <string>fetch</string>
            <string>remote-notification</string>
        </array>

        <key>NSUserNotificationUsageDescription</key>
        <string>We use notifications to remind you before your food expires.</string>
